% Demo purpose: show a source-located undefined Surface reference.
% Expected findings: SG004 ERROR for missing_boundary.
% Geometry settings: not required; the incomplete Cell is excluded if sampled.
% Scope: independently written, simplified, and not a production reactor model.

surf system_boundary sqc 0.0 0.0 0.65

cell fuel_cell 0 fuel -missing_boundary -system_boundary
cell outside_cell 0 outside system_boundary

mat fuel -10.0
92235.09c -1.0
